quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Your greed for more has distracted you
  102,2,until you go down to your graves
  102,3,"No, indeed you will soon know"
  102,4,Certainly you will soon know
  102,5,"Indeed, If you knew the knowledge of certainty"
  102,6,you would see Hell
  102,7,then you would surely see it with the eye of certainty
  102,8,And on that Day you will be asked about the pleasures you enjoyed